## Description {#details}

This class is the base class for all object file types.

Concrete instances of this object are created by createObjectFile, which figures out which type to create.

Definition at line 229 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/objectfile-h">ObjectFile.h</a>.
